[normal]The BBA is the leading trade association for the UK banking and financial services sector. We speak for over 200 member banks from 60 countries on the full range of UK and international banking issues. 
[normal]Through 
[normal]our 
[normal]Northern Ireland Advisory Panel, the BBA m
[normal]aintains
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]regular
[normal]&#xa0;
