[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]and local industry bodies, over and ab
[normal]ove the on-going activity
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]of our
[normal] individual members. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We are pleased to have this opportunity to respond to The Northern Ireland Affairs Committee’s inquiry
[normal] into the banking structure in Northern Ireland.
[normal] Whilst it is not suitable for the BBA
[normal] to comment on the actions of individual members, we are able to provide some broader commentary around the banking sector in Northern Ireland, which we believe will be o
[normal]f assistance to the Committee.
