[normal]The data below is from the Northern Ireland chapter taken from the 
[normal]second year of annual findings from the 
[normal]SME Finance Monitor (SMEF).
[normal]The results for Northern Ireland are based on 751 interviews (250 per quarter) in Q4 2011, to a profile by size and sector weighted to BIS profile data. 
[normal]This data provides insight into 
[normal]businesses experience as regards finance access in Northern Ireland and serves as a very useful barometer of actual business views.
