[normal]Detailed regional lending data[bold]&#xa0;[bold]The BBA provides quarterly aggregated lending statistics, in confidence, to the Department for Finance and Personnel (DFP) 
[normal]and the Economic Advisory Group (EAG) to aid understanding of credit distribution
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]in the local SME market.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]We also supply quarterly aggregated agricultural data to help the Northern Ireland Executive establish a
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]better understanding
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]of income factors affec
[normal]ting farmers.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]The BBA is also working with the banks and Northern Ireland government upon how this data may be expanded. In addition, as highlighted above, the major banks fund the independent work BDRC Continental undertake 
[normal]to assess
[normal] businesses experience
[normal] with finance. 
